leGothic,sans-serif\"><strong>▣ 첫째</strong>- 큰 그릇에 채썰은 생강,사과, 꿀을 넣고 골고루 섞어주세요.</span></p> \n <blockquote class=\"tx-quote-tistory\"> \n  <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">&nbsp;* 시간이 지나면 사과,생강에서 물이 나오니 꿀을 많이 넣지 않아도 됩니다.</span></p>\n </blockquote> \n <p style=\"FLOAT: none; TEXT-ALIGN: center; CLEAR: none\"><span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://m1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile30.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F21194645544FB5DD35FF2F\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> </p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"><strong>▣ 둘째</strong> - 이때 사과가 부서지지 않게 조심~ 조심~ 섞어주세요.</span></p> \n <div style=\"MARGIN: 17px 0px 17px -2px\" align=\"center\"> \n  <script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"http://cfs.tistory.com/custom/blog/154/1542025/skin/images/AdsenseM_ctr.js\"></script> \n </div> \n <p style=\"FLOAT: none; TEXT-ALIGN: center; CLEAR: none\"><span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://m1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile21.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F21243D45544FB5DD2480F6\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> </p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: left\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"><strong>▣ 셋째</strong> - 깨끗하고 물기가 없는 용기에 담아 10일정도 서늘하고 그늘진곳에 익힌(?) 후 드시면 됩니다.</span></p> \n <p style=\"FLOAT: none; TEXT-ALIGN: center; CLEAR: none\"><span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://m1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile4.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F23364E45544FB5DE095059\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> </p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">올 겨울 감기를 예방시켜줄 '생강차'입니다.</span></p> \n <p style=\"FLOAT: none; TEXT-ALIGN: center; CLEAR: none\"><span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://m1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile25.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F263E3445544FB5DE016254\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> </p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">생강의 매운맛이 진하면&nbsp;마시기 부담스러운데</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">&nbsp;사과나 레몬을 함께 넣으면</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">상큼하고 달콤한&nbsp;맛이&nbsp;더해져 매운맛이 전혀 부담스럽지 않게 됩니다.&nbsp;</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"FLOAT: none; TEXT-ALIGN: center; CLEAR: none\"><span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://m1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile21.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F2109963E544FB5DF08FA98\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> </p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">꿀을 얼마나 넣을까하다가 내용물의 반정도만 넣어 줬는데요.</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">단맛이 강한것도 싫기도하고 다음날 보니 생강과 사과에서 물이 나와 한병 꽉차게 되었어라고요.</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"FLOAT: none; TEXT-ALIGN: center; CLEAR: none\"><span class=\"imageblock\"> <img class=\"item_image able_slideshow\" src=\"http://m1.daumcdn.net/thumb/R750x0/?fname=http%3A%2F%2Fcfile23.uf.tistory.com%2Fimage%2F2278523E544FB5DF2274BD\" alt=\"이미지\"> </span> </p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">어제는 정말 겨울 코트를 입어야할 정도로 추워서 감기기운이 살짝 돌아~</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">아직 제대로 익지 않았는데 타봤어요.</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">물에 동동 뜨는 사과는 차를 마시면서 자연스럽게 먹게되는데요.</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">상큼하고 아삭해서 좋으네요.</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\">겨울철 감기에 좋은 음식!! 감기 예방 음식! 으로 생강차&nbsp;추천합니다.</span></p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\">&nbsp;</p> \n <div class=\"txc-textbox\" style=\"BORDER-TOP: #fefeb8 1px solid; BORDER-RIGHT: #fefeb8 1px solid; BORDER-BOTTOM: #fefeb8 1px solid; PADDING-BOTTOM: 10px; PADDING-TOP: 10px; PADDING-LEFT: 10px; BORDER-LEFT: #fefeb8 1px solid; PADDING-RIGHT: 10px; BACKGROUND-COLOR: #fefeb8\"> \n  <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #ff5e00\">&lt;집에 대추가 많다면 대추를 넣은 '생강차 만드는법 '&gt;</span></strong></span></p> \n  <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><strong></strong>&nbsp;</p> \n  <p style=\"TEXT-ALIGN: center\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #00d8ff\">제목 클릭 ==&gt;&nbsp;</span></strong></span><a href=\"http://amyzzung.tistory.com/170\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 11pt; FONT-FAMILY: Gulim,굴림,AppleGothic,sans-serif\"><strong><span style=\"FONT-SIZE: 12pt; COLOR: #00d8ff\">감기예방!!! '생강차 만드는법'</span></strong></span><